            14 (Summary Scorecard) are all new additions. This is a
            complete restructuring of the document and it is aligned
            with the v2 template.<br>
            <br>
            <b>This is the level of quality that should have been in the
              first submission.</b> That said, the first submission was
            made on 2 April — eight days before the current date — and
            Seenivasan had eight days to review it and provide feedback.
            No IST feedback was provided. I will address that separately
